\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Now, in period 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 the value of being incumbent 
\begin_inset Formula $I_{s}$
\end_inset

 or opposition 
\begin_inset Formula $O_{s}$
\end_inset

