\lambda_{2}\frac{\partial B\left(\boldsymbol{t}_{2}^{*},\boldsymbol{\tau}_{2}\right)}{\partial\tau_{k,2}}+\frac{\partial Q\left(\boldsymbol{t}_{2}^{*},\boldsymbol{\tau}_{2}\right)}{\partial\tau_{k,2}}-\lambda_{1}\frac{\partial\mathcal{F}\left(\boldsymbol{\tau}_{1},\boldsymbol{\tau}_{2}\right)}{\partial\tau_{k,2}} & \leqslant0\\
