\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{i}$
\end_inset

 is the outcome, 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{i}$
\end_inset

 is a dummy for the simplification treatment, 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{j}$
\end_inset

 are the additional treatments (deterrence, tax morale), and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{X}_{i}$
\end_inset

 are controls including gender, couples, age, region, mother tongue, number
 of children, wave dummies for treatments sent in waves.
