\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Exercise 1: Quantify the diverging views on what informal firms are
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\emph on
Survival view
\emph default
: Firms too unproductive to ever be formal even with no costs of formality
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\emph on
Parasite view:
\emph default
 Firms that could be formal but choose to be informal because it's more
 profitable
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\emph on
De Soto's view: 
\emph default
Firms that would be formal if entry costs were low enough
\end_layout

